# SmartCart AI 🛒

> An AI-powered grocery e-commerce platform that predicts product refill dates and provides personalized recommendations based on purchase history.

🔗 **Live Demo**: [https://smart-cart-drab-eight.vercel.app/]

---

## Features

- 🔐 JWT Authentication (Register / Login)
- 🛍️ Product listing with search and category filter
- 🛒 Cart system with quantity controls
- 📦 Order placement with stock management
- 🔮 AI refill prediction based on consumption analysis
- 💡 Collaborative filtering recommendation engine
- 📊 Smart dashboard with order history and spending analytics

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React.js |
| Backend | Node.js + Express |
| Database | MongoDB Atlas |
| AI Module | Python + FastAPI |
| Auth | JWT + bcrypt |
| Deployment | Vercel + Render |

---

## AI Logic

### Refill Prediction
Calculates average daily consumption per product:
```
Daily Consumption = Total Quantity Purchased / Number of Days
Next Refill Date = Last Purchase Date + (Last Quantity / Daily Consumption)
```

### Recommendation Engine
Collaborative filtering — finds users with similar purchase patterns and recommends products they bought that the current user hasn't tried.

