## Local Setup

### 1. Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Aayushh-18/SmartCart.git
cd SmartCart
```

### 2. Backend
```bash
cd backend
npm install
# Create .env with MONGO_URI and JWT_SECRET
npm run dev
```

### 3. AI Module
```bash
cd ai-module
pip install fastapi uvicorn pymongo pandas scikit-learn
python -m uvicorn app:app --reload --port 5001
```

### 4. Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
```

